Covert Skins.lore: One part firearm, two parts Trapper Keeper

Classified Skins.desc: It has been inlaid with gold and nickel and engraved with the image of a jinn.
Classified Skins.lore: Be careful what you wish for

Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted white and green and detailed with heat-transfer decals.
Classified Skins.lore: For enough money, Elite Crew will take any cause on as their own

Classified Skins.desc: It's a banana.
Classified Skins.lore: Sometimes it's ok to play with your food

Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted with the image of a skull and roots using high-durability enamel paints.
Restricted Skins.lore: There are some roots you don't want to take hold

Restricted Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Pole Position
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a red and grey racing theme.
Restricted Skins.lore: We only get one chance at this, let's do it right - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Restricted Skins.name: UMP-45 | Grand Prix
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with an old-fashioned racing motif.
Restricted Skins.lore: Don't forget your helmet

Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to look as though it just came out of the forge.
Restricted Skins.lore: Make some outlines of your own

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Turn some heads before you take them off

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P250 | Valence
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in a modern blue and grey design that complements the weapon's form.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Your skills aren't in question, your attitude is - The Teacher and The Iconoclast Part 1

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It takes time to build something beautiful, but only a moment to destroy it

Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in an Egyptian theme.
Covert Skins.lore: Its trigger weighs lighter than a feather

Covert Skins.name: M4A1-S | Chantico's Fire
Covert Skins.desc: It has been hand painted in vibrant colors and accentuated by a smiley face on the stock.
Covert Skins.lore: Protect what is yours

Classified Skins.name: UMP-45 | Primal Saber
Classified Skins.desc: It has been given a decal of a sabertooth tiger skull
Classified Skins.lore: Every predator eventually meets their end

Classified Skins.name: P250 | Asiimov
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.
Classified Skins.lore: If you think I need a rifle to kill a man, you have no idea who you're talking to... - Mikha Biton, Phoenix Sniper

Classified Skins.name: AUG | Fleet Flock
Classified Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of birds flying through clouds.
Classified Skins.lore: Some birds represent harmony and peace... these are not those birds

Restricted Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Red Astor
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with red and white accents.
Restricted Skins.lore: Booth has become synonymous with family drama; and who has time for drama when we're talking business - Huxley, The Competition

Restricted Skins.name: Galil AR | Firefight
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given crimson accents and a hand painted icon.
Restricted Skins.lore: Booth had this weapon commissioned for Valeria in an attempt to smooth things over with the Phoenix

Restricted Skins.name: Tec-9 | Re-Entry
Restricted Skins.desc: The barrel has been given a flame decal.
Restricted Skins.lore: I hate being right all the time - Carmen Cocinero, Extraction Expert

Restricted Skins.name: XM1014 | Black Tie
Restricted Skins.desc: A vision in black and white chrome, this shotgun is best used on formal occasions.
Restricted Skins.lore: We have Izaki and Cocinero. You need them for anything or can I just kill them now? - The Mercenary and The Serpent Part 1

Restricted Skins.name: SSG 08 | Ghost Crusader
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been painted white and given arctic blue accents.
Restricted Skins.lore: I can never replace what was taken from us... but I can take even more from them - The Phoenix and The Initiate Part 2

Mil-Spec Skins.name: G3SG1 | Orange Crash
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Stencils and orange spray paint gave this rifle its signature look.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Become a modern day Shere Khan

Mil-Spec Skins.name: M249 | Spectre
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted in a sleek and contemporary manner.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The Phoenix civil war is about to begin

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Fubar
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: This well-traveled shotgun has tick marks carved into the barrel.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It starts with a bang... it ends with silence

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP9 | Bioleak
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Varying shades of green create the illusion of a chemical spill.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P2000 | Oceanic
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a black base coat then accented with blue designs.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Has anyone heard from Kotaro or Carmen? - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Ventilators
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: These pistols have been elegantly painted in chrome.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: A weapon for artists, by artists

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SG 553 | Atlas
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a modern camouflage hydrographic.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It was once a design earmarked for the Coalition Taskforce, but Huxley engaged in corporate espionage to make it a Phoenix exclusive

Covert Skins.desc: It has been given an eclectic mix of hydrographic decals then drip painted.
Covert Skins.lore: No suicide squad would be complete without it

Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom designed by renowned artist Syd Mead.
Classified Skins.lore: In the past he gave us visions of the future; in the present he placed the future in our hands...

Classified Skins.name: Tec-9 | Fuel Injector
Classified Skins.desc: The body has been painted yellow and the magazine has been given a belt engine hydrographic. A hand-stitched leather grip completes this Seattle classic.

Classified Skins.name: MP9 | Airlock
Classified Skins.desc: It has been painted white and given a stark red magazine.

Restricted Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Directive
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been designed to help the future of law enforcement stop creeps.
Restricted Skins.lore: Your move...

Restricted Skins.name: SG 553 | Triarch
Restricted Skins.desc: This rifle was commissioned by royalty and given custom desert camo.
Restricted Skins.lore: Remind them of your love

Restricted Skins.name: MAG-7 | Petroglyph
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted to give the illusion of a rock craving.
Restricted Skins.lore: Conflict existed since the first caveman learned how to pick up a rock – Booth, Arms Dealer

Restricted Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Powercore
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in green with yellow accents, then given a USB code for quick checkout.
Restricted Skins.lore: Rule No. 1 – Challenge demands satisfaction

Restricted Skins.name: Glock-18 | Weasel
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of Bobby the Mischievous Weasel. Don't mess with Bobby.
Restricted Skins.lore: Just because he's cute, doesn't mean he doesn't bite

Mil-Spec Skins.name: XM1014 | Slipstream
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with smoky greys and vibrant blues.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Patience, Elliott; they still have a role to play... - The Mercenary and The Serpent Part 2

Mil-Spec Skins.name: G3SG1 | Ventilator
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given an elegant black and chrome paintjob and a custom rubber stock.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Don't worry Naomi, I'll make Felix pay - Mikha Biton, Phoenix Sniper

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P90 | Grim
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of murderous specters, then dry brushed with green accents.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Imogen... are you selling me a gun or a velvet poster? – Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Negev | Dazzle
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been covered in blue and white zebra stripe decals.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Finally, a gun for trivia lovers

Mil-Spec Skins.name: UMP-45 | Briefing
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of a topographical map.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: This is going to be a short meeting...

Mil-Spec Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Imprint
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painstakingly etched by hand.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Couture firearms have taken the Czech Republic by storm

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Scumbria
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been discretely painted with stripes.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: You can't leave him to die, Felix; you have to save him - The Daughter and the Paladin Part 1

Restricted Skins.desc: It has silver filigree appliqués over an light blue anodized base.

Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a graphic design in violet and black.

Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been decorated with riveted metal panels.

Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a red and purple hydrographic over a metallic base coat.

Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been decorated with a bio-mechanical motif.

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Hedge Maze
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The green and white gloves were manufactured by Icarus Athletics.
Rare Special Items.lore: Only cowards fear flying close to the sun

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Driver Gloves | Diamondback
Rare Special Items.desc: These driving gloves offer protection from the elements while still maintaining tactile sensation. It has been crafted out of a mix of tan leather, black leather, and snakeskin.
Rare Special Items.lore: Standard issue is for suckers... - Imogen, Arms Dealer In Training

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Boom!
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. This pair has been covered in comic book onomatopoeia.
Rare Special Items.lore: POW! BOOM! BIFF!

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Hand Wraps | Slaughter
Rare Special Items.desc: Preferred by hand-to-hand fighters, these wraps protect the knuckles and stabilize the wrist when punching. Dyed crimson, these wraps make it hard to see where the fabric ends and the bloodstains begin
Rare Special Items.lore: Who doesn't love working with their hands?

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Driver Gloves | Lunar Weave
Rare Special Items.desc: These driving gloves offer protection from the elements while still maintaining tactile sensation. Midnight blue suede has been interwoven with jet black leather to give these gloves a timeless look.
Rare Special Items.lore: Keeps the blood off your hands...metaphorically speaking

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Hand Wraps | Leather
Rare Special Items.desc: Preferred by hand-to-hand fighters, these wraps protect the knuckles and stabilize the wrist when punching. They are made of leather, gauze, and wicked intent.
Rare Special Items.lore: Become notorious

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Guerrilla
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. It was made with a mix of brown leather and synthetic leather with a camo print.
Rare Special Items.lore: Valeria plans on retribution, of that there can be no doubt... - Sebastien Hennequet, Sniper

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Crimson Kimono
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. This pair of black gloves has been accented with a stark red diamond pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: Start seeing red

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Bronzed
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. The leather has been dyed gun metal and bronze.
Rare Special Items.lore: Operation Bloodhound marked the end of rouge sniper Chase Turner

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Spearmint
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. White leather and red stitching make these gloves as stylish as they are comfortable.
Rare Special Items.lore: For what he's charging us, you'd think Huxley could at least throw in a tin of mints... - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Eclipse
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. This is the original classic black design that made Tortue a household name.
Rare Special Items.lore: Don't call it a midlife crisis

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Cool Mint
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. The soft blue leather has been accented with arctic colored geometric designs.
Rare Special Items.lore: Combat has never felt so refreshing.

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Driver Gloves | Crimson Weave
Rare Special Items.desc: These driving gloves offer protection from the elements while still maintaining tactile sensation. Black suede has been interwoven with scarlet leather to give these gloves a timeless look.
Rare Special Items.lore: Leave your mark, not your fingerprints

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Foundation
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. The white and black gloves have been given orange accents
Rare Special Items.lore: Rumor has it that Tortue was inspired by the Asiimov line of firearms

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Snakebite
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. It was crafted with a mix of leather and snakeskin.
Rare Special Items.lore: Let's be honest... no one misses Sergei - Hans Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. The hand stitched leather has been paired with rugged DDPAT printed fabric.
Rare Special Items.lore: Some people don't like getting their hands dirty

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Driver Gloves | Convoy
Rare Special Items.desc: These driving gloves offer protection from the elements while still maintaining tactile sensation. It has been made with a mix of brown soft leather and dyed suede.
Rare Special Items.lore: Sometimes discretion is called for

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Emerald Web
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. The back of the gloves have been given a spiderweb pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: Discipline begets success

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Superconductor
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The blue and black gloves are ideal for those who wish to be phenomenal.
Rare Special Items.lore: They don't want none

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Arid
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. Multiple shades of brown and a subtle camo print give these gloves a distinguished look.
Rare Special Items.lore: If we're going to be heroes, we may as well look the part... - Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Hand Wraps | Spruce DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: Preferred by hand-to-hand fighters, these wraps protect the knuckles and stabilize the wrist when punching. The outer wrap is fabric screen printed with grey digital camo.
Rare Special Items.lore: Some people say they're tough... others show it

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Charred
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. It was crafted out of classic black supple leather.
Rare Special Items.lore: Challenge coins are great, but they don't draw blood when you backfist someone - Carmen Cocinero, Extraction Expert

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Pandora's Box
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The black and purple gloves have a subtle pattern printed on the palms.
Rare Special Items.lore: A must have for any demolitions expert with sweaty palms

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Hand Wraps | Badlands
Rare Special Items.desc: Preferred by hand-to-hand fighters, these wraps protect the knuckles and stabilize the wrist when punching. This DIY hand protection is made of scavenged materials.
Rare Special Items.lore: Felix turns a blind eye towards the Colation Taskforce's unsanctioned boxing league

Covert Skins.name: SSG 08 | Dragonfire
Covert Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of a monstrous dragon snorting fire.
Covert Skins.lore: Sit on your horde and wait for any who come to take it

Covert Skins.name: M4A4 | Buzz Kill
Covert Skins.desc: This Sektor Industry firearm has been sleekly painted in yellow and green.
Covert Skins.lore: There's one at every party

Classified Skins.name: P90 | Shallow Grave
Classified Skins.desc: The grips have been painted to resemble rune stones, and a hydrographic of a skeleton has been applied to the stock.
Classified Skins.lore: With the amount of bodies you're racking up, who has time to dig?

Classified Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Wasteland Princess
Classified Skins.desc: Someone has been keeping track of kills on the barrel.
Classified Skins.lore: A perfect gift for the sociopath that has everything...

Restricted Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Royal Consorts

Restricted Skins.lore: Face off and release the doves

Restricted Skins.name: G3SG1 | Stinger
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been given yellow and grey accents.
Restricted Skins.lore: A moment of pain. Then nothing.

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Crimson Kimono
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. This pair of black gloves has been accented with a stark red diamond pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: Start seeing red

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Bronzed
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. The leather has been dyed gun metal and bronze.
Rare Special Items.lore: Operation Bloodhound marked the end of rouge sniper Chase Turner

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Spearmint
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. White leather and red stitching make these gloves as stylish as they are comfortable.
Rare Special Items.lore: For what he's charging us, you'd think Huxley could at least throw in a tin of mints... - Felix Riley, Commanding Officer

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Eclipse
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. This is the original classic black design that made Tortue a household name.
Rare Special Items.lore: Don't call it a midlife crisis

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Moto Gloves | Cool Mint
Rare Special Items.desc: These bulky hard knuckled gloves can protect the wearers hands from road rash at 60 mph. The soft blue leather has been accented with arctic colored geometric designs.
Rare Special Items.lore: Combat has never felt so refreshing.

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Driver Gloves | Crimson Weave
Rare Special Items.desc: These driving gloves offer protection from the elements while still maintaining tactile sensation. Black suede has been interwoven with scarlet leather to give these gloves a timeless look.
Rare Special Items.lore: Leave your mark, not your fingerprints

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Foundation
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. The white and black gloves have been given orange accents
Rare Special Items.lore: Rumor has it that Tortue was inspired by the Asiimov line of firearms

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Snakebite
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. It was crafted with a mix of leather and snakeskin.
Rare Special Items.lore: Let's be honest... no one misses Sergei - Hans Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Forest DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. The hand stitched leather has been paired with rugged DDPAT printed fabric.
Rare Special Items.lore: Some people don't like getting their hands dirty

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Driver Gloves | Convoy
Rare Special Items.desc: These driving gloves offer protection from the elements while still maintaining tactile sensation. It has been made with a mix of brown soft leather and dyed suede.
Rare Special Items.lore: Sometimes discretion is called for

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Specialist Gloves | Emerald Web
Rare Special Items.desc: Durable, breathable, and stylish; these gloves are designed to take (and give) a beating. The back of the gloves have been given a spiderweb pattern.
Rare Special Items.lore: Discipline begets success

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Superconductor
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The blue and black gloves are ideal for those who wish to be phenomenal.
Rare Special Items.lore: They don't want none

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Arid
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. Multiple shades of brown and a subtle camo print give these gloves a distinguished look.
Rare Special Items.lore: If we're going to be heroes, we may as well look the part... - Rona Sabri, Rising Star

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Hand Wraps | Spruce DDPAT
Rare Special Items.desc: Preferred by hand-to-hand fighters, these wraps protect the knuckles and stabilize the wrist when punching. The outer wrap is fabric screen printed with grey digital camo.
Rare Special Items.lore: Some people say they're tough... others show it

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Bloodhound Gloves | Charred
Rare Special Items.desc: These fingerless gloves have been decorated with metal studs and the Operation Bloodhound logo. It was crafted out of classic black supple leather.
Rare Special Items.lore: Challenge coins are great, but they don't draw blood when you backfist someone - Carmen Cocinero, Extraction Expert

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Sport Gloves | Pandora's Box
Rare Special Items.desc: Synthetic fabrics make these athletic gloves durable and eye-catching. The black and purple gloves have a subtle pattern printed on the palms.
Rare Special Items.lore: A must have for any demolitions expert with sweaty palms

Rare Special Items.name: ★ Hand Wraps | Badlands
Rare Special Items.desc: Preferred by hand-to-hand fighters, these wraps protect the knuckles and stabilize the wrist when punching. This DIY hand protection is made of scavenged materials.
Rare Special Items.lore: Felix turns a blind eye towards the Colation Taskforce's unsanctioned boxing league

Covert Skins.name: AWP | Oni Taiji
Covert Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with colorful samurai and Oni imagery.
Covert Skins.lore: Face your demons

Covert Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Hyper Beast
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a beastly creature in psychedelic colors.
Covert Skins.lore: We're all monsters

Classified Skins.name: Dual Berettas | Cobra Strike
Classified Skins.desc: A cobra has been hand painted on either grip. The slide displays its neon venom.

Classified Skins.name: M4A4 | Hellfire
Classified Skins.desc: A devil-like creature has been hand painted among fire and chains.

Classified Skins.name: Galil AR | Sugar Rush
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using cotton candy themed colors and various patterns.

Restricted Skins.name: SSG 08 | Death's Head
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted to resemble a death's-head hawkmoth.
Restricted Skins.lore: Quid pro quo

Restricted Skins.name: P250 | Red Rock
Restricted Skins.desc: A custom DDPAT camouflage with yellows and oranges has been applied.
Restricted Skins.lore: Just over the horizon

Restricted Skins.name: AK-47 | Orbit Mk01
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with a red and black design.
Restricted Skins.lore: Recovered from COLONY01

Restricted Skins.name: P90 | Death Grip
Restricted Skins.desc: A hydrographic pattern of overlapping hands has been applied to a blue base.
Restricted Skins.lore: Do not go quietly

Restricted Skins.name: P2000 | Woodsman
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with custom green camouflage and orange detailing.
Restricted Skins.lore: "The orange is for you, not me"

Mil-Spec Skins.name: UMP-45 | Metal Flowers
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a steel-colored pattern of funeral roses.

Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been given a hydrographic of a topographical map.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Tec-9 | Cut Out

Mil-Spec Skins.name: USP-S | Blueprint

Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Sometimes the best-laid plans go awry

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAC-10 | Aloha
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been airbrushed with a red hibiscus pattern.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAG-7 | Hard Water
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted with a grey anodized pattern and finished with blue highlights.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: FAMAS | Macabre
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray painted with a green design over a yellow undercoat.
